<h3 id="1-programming-and-sql">1) Programming and SQL</h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://youtu.be/lj724M9dC4M">Python - Corey Schafer Playlist</a> (Focus on <strong>13</strong>, <strong>18-32</strong>, <strong>35-45</strong>)</li>
