  <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZyhVh-qRZPA&amp;list=PL-osiE80TeTsWmV9i9c58mdDCSskIFdDS">Pandas by Corey Schafer</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.hackerearth.com/practice/machine-learning/data-manipulation-visualisation-r-python/tutorial-data-manipulation-numpy-pandas-python/tutorial/">Numpy</a></li>
</ul>

