  <li>Basics of Tableau</li>
  <li><a href="https://towardsdatascience.com/hitchhikers-guide-to-exploratory-data-analysis-6e8d896d3f7e">Hitchhikerâ€™s guide to Exploratory Data Analysis</a></li>
  <li>A sample project</li>
</ul>

